    • Method Detail

      • add

        public static void add​(java.lang.String resource)
        Adds a tile set resource to the list of tile set files. If the tile set has not been added previously, its entries will be parsed and added to the available tiles.
        Parameters:
        resource - the location of the tile set resource

      • getTileSets
